{"tid":1939674,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利物浦球員們怕冠軍飛走 接受心理輔導緩解焦慮","createTime":"2020-03-23T09:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T03:19:13.000Z","uid":173952,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4aabc076ea81c6ab546ec06f6066804652517051","tid":1939674,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:19:54.000Z","msg":"據英國媒體報導，利物浦球會向自己的球員們提供心理健康支持，緩解他們擔心拿不到英超冠軍的焦慮。<br />\n<br />\n  《每日郵報》披露，紅軍球會體育心理學專家李-理查森製作了這份視頻文件，並給球員們進行輔導。很多隊員擔憂，英超賽季作廢，原本到手的冠軍可能會拿不到，對此，該視頻開導球員們：「英超的決定或者疫情的走向，是不在我們掌控中的，我們能掌控的是自己的行為和反應。專注於我們能掌控的，接受我們無法掌控的。」<br />\n<br />\n  球員們被鼓勵在焦慮時採用腹式呼吸法，視頻還教導球員們：「足球不是最重要的，健康和安全才是。」"},{"pid":"9e02eafc1a5d5148efe99f61aab1299c17322685","tid":1939674,"uid":308486,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T10:03:21.000Z","msg":"睇黎利迷都需要接受心理輔導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4245a33b114394bf728c42813ae221f34e16bc3a","tid":1939674,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e02eafc1a5d5148efe99f61aab1299c17322685","tid":1939674,"uid":308486,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T10:03:21.000Z","msg":"睇黎利迷都需要接受心理輔導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T10:37:10.000Z","msg":"我地享受過程"},{"pid":"b66fbbc7ba273a2f1c38b481a469c6d91abe0cb1","tid":1939674,"uid":199081,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9e02eafc1a5d5148efe99f61aab1299c17322685","tid":1939674,"uid":308486,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T10:03:21.000Z","msg":"睇黎利迷都需要接受心理輔導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:43:26.000Z","msg":"利迷先唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=